<p>(b)"User&rdquo; or &ldquo;you" means any person who accesses or uses the Apka Budget for his own purpose or on behalf of someone else and includes any legal entity.</p>
<p>(c)&ldquo;User&rsquo;s Content&rdquo; means any content, including any text, data, information or other material, that you may upload, transmit or store using the functionality of the Apka Budget.</p>
<p>(d)&ldquo;Order&rdquo; or "Job": means any order placed for services through the Apka Budget Mobile Application/Website or any other medium or platform.</p>
<p>(e) &ldquo;Agreed Time&rdquo; means the appointed date and time for your services to be provided and as mentioned in the registration form.</p>
<p>(f)"Vendor" wherever applicable means a third party, which has agreed to co-operate with Apka Budget to offer its services.</p>
