<h2><span style="color: rgb(53, 152, 219);">Acceptance of Terms</span></h2>
<p>The terms and conditions set forth below ("Terms of Use") constitute a legally-binding agreement between Apka Budget and you. These Terms of Use contain provisions that define your limits, legal rights and obligations with respect to your use of and participation in &ldquo;Apka Budget&rdquo; website or mobile App. User is hereby accept all the term and condition are mentioned below</p>
<h2><span style="color: rgb(53, 152, 219);">Apkabudget Services Use</span></h2>
<p>User is hereby allowed to use the Apka Budget subject to acceptance of the terms and conditions of this Terms of Use and the Privacy Policy on the Apka Budget App and/or Website (&ldquo;Terms&rdquo;). User conveys acceptance to Terms every time the User uses the Apka Budget. User has discretion not to use the Apka Budget, so User&rsquo;s use of the Apka Budget, despite having the right and power of not to use, is construed as User has accepted the Terms.</p>
<p>Apka Budget can provide User, subject to acceptance of Terms, at its sole discretion, the User Name and Password (&ldquo;User Account&rdquo;). Apka Budget solely reserves the right to accept or reject application made by User for having User Account without obligation of explanation. Apka Budget&nbsp;reserves the right to store, evaluate, analyses, verify and authenticate the personal information and data provided by the User. The User hereby acknowledges that Apka Budget continues to maintain right to close the User Account without any prior notice for any reasons whatsoever it may be.</p>
<h2><span style="color: rgb(53, 152, 219);">Modification to Terms and Services</span></h2>
<p>Apka Budget retains the right to change the Terms from time to time and such modified Terms shall be immediately applicable. Every time You use the Apka Budget, shall constitute your acceptance of changes made to Terms Your use of the Website following any amendment of the Terms of Use will signify your assent to and acceptance of any revised Terms of Use. If you do not agree to abide by these or any future Terms of Use, please do not use or access the Website</p>
<h2><span style="color: rgb(53, 152, 219);">Eligibility and Accessibility</span></h2>
<p>Use of the Website is available only to individuals who are at least 18 years old and can form legally binding contracts under applicable law. You represent, acknowledge and agree that you are at least 18 years of age and to be legally capable of entering into a legal contract and has understood and voluntarily accepted the Terms.</p>
<p>You will be issued a user id and password to access your account. You must keep password confidential and not share it with any other person. You are responsible for all activity on your account, whether or not you authorized it. However, if you become aware of any unauthorized use of your account or your user id and password, please contact us immediately.</p>
<h2><span style="color: rgb(53, 152, 219);">Rules Of Conduct</span></h2>
<p>The ApkaBudget shall facilitate the User to order or book services online by using the ApkaBudget App and/or Website or calls. You acknowledge, agree that you have complete responsibility while ordering services through the ApkaBudget App and/or Website or calls. The User&rsquo;s discretion is required while using the ApkaBudget.</p>
<p>The ApkaBudget shall be used solely for User&rsquo;s non-exclusive, non-assignable, non-transferable and limited personal use and for no other purposes.</p>
<p>User&rsquo;s Use of the Apka Budget is subject to all applicable local, state, national laws and regulations wherever applicable. Except as specifically permitted in Terms, User shall have no right to copy, change, alter, amend, reverse engineer, decompile, reverse translate, disassemble, publish, disclose, display or make available, or in any other manner, decode the Apka Budget App and/or the Website.</p>
<h2><span style="color: rgb(53, 152, 219);">Ordering</span></h2>
<p>You agree that, any contract for the service ordered through use of Apka Budget App/ Website or calls is between &ldquo;You&rdquo; and &ldquo;Apka Budget&rdquo;, any contract for the supply of Apka Budget from the Apka Budget App and/or Website is between &ldquo;You&rdquo; and &ldquo;Apka Budget&rdquo;. You agree to take reasonable care when providing Apka Budget with your details and warrant that these details are accurate and complete at the time of ordering a service. Apka Budget and/or Services purchased/availed from theApka Budget App and/or Website is intended for your use only and that &ldquo;You&rdquo; are acting as an end customer only and not as an agent for another party while using the Apka Budget.</p>
<p>You understand that some type of services may be suitable for Users within certain age ranges and gender only unless mentioned otherwise. It is your sole responsibility to check whether the service you are ordering is suitable for the intended recipient.</p>
<p>You understand that, if the ordered service is within the capacity of the Apka Budget or it's associated vendors, Apka Budget will accept the contract and confirm it to you. If the details of the order are correct, the contract for the service will be confirmed by text message (SMS) and/or other medium to the User.</p>
<p>In case the service offered by Apka Budget is ordered, Apka Budget will confirm availability together with or separately from service.</p>
<p>The confirmation message will specify delivery details including the approximate service time specified by Apka Budget.</p>
<p>In case service is not possible for whatsoever reason, Apka Budget will let you know by text message (SMS), phone call and/or other medium. You understand and acknowledge that in unforeseeable events or Force Majeure events, Apka Budget may not be able to reach and/or communicate with you about the non-availability of the scheduled service.</p>
<h2><span style="color: rgb(53, 152, 219);">Prices And Payment</span></h2>
<p>All prices listed on the Apka Budget App and/or Website for services are correct at the time of publication and is as received vendors wherever applicable. While Apka Budget takes great care to keep them up to date</p>
<p>Visit Charge: Visit charge will be applicable on every order if customer denies to allow technician to complete the task after the visit. Its means once technician reached at customer place and client denied to accept solution then client have to pay minimum visiting charges which is mentioned in price list of every service category.</p>
<p>You will make payment in full to Service provider introduced to you through us for any services provided by such Service provider to you. You shall be required to pay the minimum charges or Repair charges along with the spare parts costs (whichever is high), if any installed or replaced / substituted in the products, to the Service Provider and the minimum service charges rates can be found on the Website of the Company. The Service charges shall be updated or amended from time to time and it shall be your responsibility to remain informed about the prevailing minimum charges for the services. And you should confirm the same from the Service provider about the service charge for the repair of the products before initiation of the Service. You agree that you will pay for all services you avail from the Service Provider either by way of cash, cheque, online payment, or any other payment method introduced by the company. Any payment made is non-refundable. After the completion of the Service, the final price charged to you by Apka Budget or the vendor may change at the time of delivery based on the latest menu and prices. Apka Budget&nbsp;reserves the right to alter the menu of the services available for usage on the Apka Budget App and/or Website and to delete and remove them if needed.</p>
<p>All prices listed on the Apka Budget App and/or Website for services by Apka Budget or its associated vendors listed on the Apka Budget App and/or Website reflect the price charged by Apka Budget or the vendor or its service partner at the time of listing. In the event where the vendor or the service partner informs Apka Budget immediately after placing the order by the User, about the change in price for the service, Apka Budget&nbsp;will try to make every possible effort to inform the User about the price difference and the User can choose to opt-out of the order at that time</p>
<p>The final cost towards the service will be confirmed after the inspection/ visit and before commencement of the service. Full payment must be made for all the particulars mentioned in the order. Payment has to be made in cash or, if available on the Apka Budget App and/or Website, by online payment including through credit card, debit card, net banking or wallet.</p>
<p>If you choose online payment, you must pay for your order before it is delivered. You shall ensure that online payment mode is secured, your debit/credit card details will be encrypted to prevent the possibility of someone being able to read them as they are sent over the internet. Your credit card company may also conduct necessary security checks to confirm about your identification before making any such payment.</p>
<h2><span style="color: rgb(53, 152, 219);">Service</span></h2>
<p>(a) The Company provides technology based services for providing home solutions in such as repairing / services of home products to you and you agree to obtain the services offered by third party technicians / Service Providers / Private Repair Professionals ("the Service Provider"). All the Services provided by the Company to you by means of your use of the registration on website of the Company are hereinafter referred to as the "Service."</p>
<p>(b) The entire Booking request as may be directed by the customer shall be forward to the concerned repair professional/service provider by the Company. The Service Provider shall be provided on availability basis and the same shall be communicated to the customer through the company internal mechanism procedure, however, it is clarified that on availability of the Service Provider, the communication details of Service Provider &amp; Customer shall be shared between both of them by the Company for the ease of both the parties to perform or exercise their rights &amp; obligations.</p>
<p>(c) In case, the Service Provider accepts the booking request made by you with the Company, your information is sent to the Service provider including your name, contact number etc. (d) Company shall endeavor reasonable efforts to bring you in contact with the Service Provider in order to render the required service subject to availability of the Service Provider in or around your location at the time of your booking request made to the Company.</p>
<p>(e) Service time quoted at the time of ordering is approximate only and may vary. Services will be delivered to the address as intimated by you while ordering. In case service is done by Company or vendor or a third party delivery service provider assigned by ApkaBudget, ApkaBudget will take reasonable care to deliver in a timely manner. No responsibility is taken for late service by ApkaBudget in either case.</p>
<p>(f) In case of a late service, no charges will either be voided or refunded by ApkaBudget.All risk in the service shall pass to you upon availing the service though ApkaBudget takes ample precaution to avoid any such risks.If you fail to accept the service at the time they are ready or ApkaBudget&nbsp;is unable to deliver at the nominated time due to your failure to provide appropriate instructions or authorizations, then the service shall be deemed to have been delivered to you and all risk and responsibility in relation to such orders shall pass to you. Any storage, insurance and other costs which ApkaBudget incurs as a result of the inability to service shall be your responsibility and you shall indemnify ApkaBudget&nbsp;in full for such cost.</p>
<p>(g) You will treat Service provider introduced to you through us with respect and not to cause damage to them or engage in any unlawful, threatening, harassing, abusive behavior or activity whilst using their service;</p>
<p>(h) Before handing over the products to be repaired the customer shall be cautious and ensure themselves about the credibility of the Service Provider and any defect in Service or theft/ damage to the asset; spare parts; accessories; products shall not be compensated by the Company in any manner whatsoever and it is clarified that that Company shall not be liable in any manner whatsoever, if any such harm/damage/ loss is caused to the Service Provider due to any such transfer or products to the Service provider for Service.You must ensure that at the time of service arrangements, including access where necessary, are in place for offering the service. ApkaBudget cannot be held liable for any damage, cost or expense incurred to such service as a result of a failure to provide adequate access or arrangements for service.</p>
<ol>
<li>To offer services at the place of service requested by you in your order;</li>
<li>To deliver within the time confirmed in your order;</li>
<li>To inform you if they expect that they are unable to meet the estimated service time.</li>
</ol>
<p>(I) ApkaBudget, the vendors or the service partners shall not be liable to you for any losses, liabilities, costs, damages, charges or expenses arising out of late delivery.</p>
<p>You understand and accept that it might not be possible for ApkaBudget, vendor or service partners to offer services to some locations. In such cases, ApkaBudget will inform you accordingly and arrange for cancellation of the order or service to any alternative delivery address.</p>
<h2><span style="color: rgb(53, 152, 219);">Information</span></h2>
<p>Where Apka Budget have requested information from you to provide service, you agree to provide Apka Budget with accurate and complete information.</p>
<p>You authorize Apka Budget to use, store or otherwise process your personal information in order to provide the service to you and for marketing and credit control purposes (the "Purpose"). The Purpose may include the disclosure of your personal information to selected third parties from time to time where Apka Budget believes that the services offered by such third parties may be of interest to you or where this is required by law or in order to provide the service to you in future You are entitled to request a copy of the said personal information Apka Budget holds about you. Please contact us if you wish to request copy of this information.</p>
